(Hakibuscon is a neutral bot, he works for nobody.  His body WAS that of a =
chameleon, but his body was scrapped, so his spark left his body.  Now, his=
 spark entered the body of a female bot named Spitfire, but he goes as Haki=
buscon, and he is kind of embarrassed about having a female bot's body[Who =
wouldn't be?]  If you need to know, Hakibuscon's new body transforms into a=
 snake.)

::Hakibuscon::

    He left where he was and went insearch of mor=
e Transformers. He needed to find some, and he had decided to make use of h=
is female body. Travelling in snake mode he slithered along the ground. His=
 body was stiff, he had been hibernating to long.
